summary:
Understood. For any ASX announcement you provide (or simulate), I will:  

1. **Quickly classify the announcement type** (e.g., Trading Halt, Capital Raising, Quarterly, M&A).  
2. **Extract only the material details** per your strict formatting rules.  
3. **Omit all fluff** (boilerplate, director names, non-impactful operational updates).  

**Example Outputs:**  

---  
**Trading Halt Request**  
• Reason: Pending capital raising announcement ($50M placement).  

**Capital Raising Announcement**  
• Structure: $100M accelerated placement + $20M SPP.  
• Key dates: Ex-date 15/05/2024, SPP closes 30/05/2024.  

**Quarterly Report (4C)**  
• Cash balance: $12.7M (vs. $15.1M last quarter).  
• Key highlight: Production +22% QoQ to 50koz Au.  

**Other Announcement**  
• Strategic review initiated; asset divestments targeting $200M.  
• CEO resigns effective immediately (no successor named).  

**No material information identified**  
---  

Ready to analyze your PDF/text. Paste or describe the announcement, and specify if you need emphasis on particular aspects (liquidity, valuation, etc.).
